description: This is just a goofy Alexa Skill that can either read back Donald Trump's latest tweet or tell you a random tweet from Donald Trump. It is not intended as support or endorsement of Donald Trump. This skill is only for novelty purposes. The skill is not sponsored or endorsed by The Trump Organization.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask President Tweets to read me his latest tweet
Alexa, ask President Tweets to tell me a random tweet
Alexa, ask President Tweets what is the last thing the president said on twitter
name: President Tweets
shortDescription: This is an Alexa Skill that reads back Donald Trump tweets
